{"tid":30132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解宜家淫閪收兵冇人屌","createTime":"2016-12-09T04:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T18:03:13.000Z","uid":48773,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5fdcc1cc48ce8654d5325174d4fe40878569dfe4","tid":30132,"uid":48773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:21:34.000Z","msg":"個撚個見到對香雞腳就狗衝去奶個MON <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開埋嗰啲乜鳩緣份計劃更加冇人屌<br />\n<br />\n收兵就死翻5P 死臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n厹都係呀 屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n影撚響哂啲風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ac112ceb511290bc7d4109ee74f1a865537a31","tid":30132,"uid":1227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:24:11.000Z","msg":"「男就post得,女post就收兵」<br />\n明眼人就明啦唔洗講咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我初初都係開post屌,冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bf394f0af91f5ec17b944f5f81d49684014e80","tid":30132,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:25:31.000Z","msg":"雞全部都係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b22e60f6e425352dc0ee1e5a8abb982989ef479","tid":30132,"uid":48773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:32:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「男就post得,女post就收兵」<br />\n明眼人就明啦唔洗講咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我初初都係開post屌,冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就黎俾班淫蟲淫閪搞撚到變質"},{"pid":"3c695b1e2b48221817471468da401efd0a306251","tid":30132,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5fa326de74f36cf4b9faffd91ae65bf2fd5b0e","tid":30132,"uid":48773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:33:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雞全部都係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我呢一刻真係好嬲 好想矯正呢個風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e75cc2aeff4ab714defe91f48dfde0b395d4a1","tid":30132,"uid":48773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:38:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/09/123732_b5cdacf745e6dea611049ec7fe5a526a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F09%2F123732_b5cdacf745e6dea611049ec7fe5a526a.jpg&h=ccf0ef8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n博乜？你話喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38731e3aeb7d0fca192901e56036f73edf0e2c99","tid":30132,"uid":31413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:38:23.000Z","msg":"依家多左女人上一定會變質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你以前邊度會有咁撚多女人上<br />\n個撚個上都唔好意思比人知<br />\n<br />\n依家唔撚同曬啦 post張腳 大把狗公奶唔切<br />\n出面講故post 貼撚埋對波就知咩事啦<br />\n<br />\n仲未撚講埋5p字 吾系甘牙 <br />\n根本全部野變撚曬<br />\n的確 依度已經唔係高登<br />\n係連登 <br />\n但我始終想同班撚樣講句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母臭閪 點解以前咁撚好睇係因為個個都遵守依套 先咁撚好睇炸 屌你老母依家你係度搞到個壇低質曬呀屌你老母 </span></span>"},{"pid":"2a07ba709b03eb7fcf4be19169f00b4abb8361cc","tid":30132,"uid":11320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:40:22.000Z","msg":"因為D想屌西既狗公佔大多數，可憐到要係網上溝女囉"},{"pid":"0cfa457a8fa9f50a2bd386bc00a899cf18a93910","tid":30132,"uid":48773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家多左女人上一定會變質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你以前邊度會有咁撚多女人上<br />\n個撚個上都唔好意思比人知<br />\n<br />\n依家唔撚同曬啦 post張腳 大把狗公奶唔切<br />\n出面講故post 貼撚埋對波就知咩事啦<br />\n<br />\n仲未撚講埋5p字 吾系甘牙 <br />\n根本全部野變撚曬<br />\n的確 依度已經唔係高登<br />\n係連登 <br />\n但我始終想同班撚樣講句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母臭閪 點解以前咁撚好睇係因為個個都遵守依套 先咁撚好睇炸 屌你老母依家你係度搞到個壇低質曬呀屌你老母 </span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明呀巴打 最弊係班撚頭人俾人用對唔知係咪肥仔波嘅波拋一拋 就拋到一地精 護主都護唔切"},{"pid":"c26aee073b5d002e1033567157f9c1fbb59ffd63","tid":30132,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:43:10.000Z","msg":"用手機app做主導就一定咁<br />\n人流多但咩人都有<br />\n出名後應該會愈黎愈多後生上"},{"pid":"156abbaba53df2ffd8ecaee2dc293a5133772c48","tid":30132,"uid":48773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為D想屌西既狗公佔大多數，可憐到要係網上溝女囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鬼唔望班所謂真絲 全撚部都係有波死肥閪 仲要背脊生哂瘡 紙袋笠頭都嫌樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d019daa125a5abc873718a06fd8d23a99c751880","tid":30132,"uid":48773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用手機app做主導就一定咁<br />\n人流多但咩人都有<br />\n出名後應該會愈黎愈多後生上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁可以點做 屌又屌唔切 屌得呢個又屌唔到嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd8f78825e8cbd3c2f81db723a203b6b2b2bcdc","tid":30132,"uid":31413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:45:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為D想屌西既狗公佔大多數，可憐到要係網上溝女囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鬼唔望班所謂真絲 全撚部都係有波死肥閪 仲要背脊生哂瘡 紙袋笠頭都嫌樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 梗係依家有堆絲根本係臭閪黎<br />\n不知幾撚享受比狗奶 <br />\n又有班精蟲上腦 見閪就屌既傻閪係度"},{"pid":"cb529c4ecb6e0a37aadad90d107beeb46edbae2b","tid":30132,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用手機app做主導就一定咁<br />\n人流多但咩人都有<br />\n出名後應該會愈黎愈多後生上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁可以點做 屌又屌唔切 屌得呢個又屌唔到嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想人流多咪呢邊<br />\n想似以前風氣多d. 咪個邊"},{"pid":"5c38947a53f1b800b45be9dfd4606b4fe53be0dd","tid":30132,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n我明呀巴打 最弊係班撚頭人俾人用對唔知係咪肥仔波嘅波拋一拋 就拋到一地精 護主都護唔切</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢D囡，人地叫佢貼佢就貼，<br />\n好打極有限<br />\n<del>畢嬲弱智都獲市場</del><br />\n<br />\n最撚憎D囡，自己貼撚完跟住又屌多狗公煩，<br />\n屌鳩佢就話「唔通著短裙比人強姦抵死？」<br />\n屌，你明知一街強姦犯你會唔會仲著短裙呀？<br />\n同理，網上肯撚定一大堆厹架啦，<br />\n仲要咁貼唔係博屌博出位我真係唔知咩原因"},{"pid":"7069120ebbd0de3321a1a9bbb7ddaa3bdf945246","tid":30132,"uid":48773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:48:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為D想屌西既狗公佔大多數，可憐到要係網上溝女囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鬼唔望班所謂真絲 全撚部都係有波死肥閪 仲要背脊生哂瘡 紙袋笠頭都嫌樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 梗係依家有堆絲根本係臭閪黎<br />\n不知幾撚享受比狗奶 <br />\n又有班精蟲上腦 見閪就屌既傻閪係度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n豬閪都係肉嘛巴打"},{"pid":"2664907166d60313dbc80beb5297271bc98a6f33","tid":30132,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:49:32.000Z","msg":"正